item.title: Babar Azam T20 World Cup runs 2022: Pakistani captain T20 World Cup innings list
item.description: Babar Azam T20 World Cup runs 2022: Pakistani captain T20 World Cup innings list Pakistan’s captain Babar Azam’s horrid T20 World Cup 2022 continued in the match against South Africa as well where he managed to score 6 runs in 15 deliveries before getting dismissed to Lungi Ngidi.
